The paper deals with graph visualization, which is a topic in computer graphics (cs.CG). It also involves the study of graph structures and algorithms for recognizing certain properties of graphs, which falls under the categories of data structures (cs.DS), graph theory (cs.GR), and computational geometry (cs.CG).
